WEBVTT

00:00.701 --> 00:01.221
Hey, look!

00:01.604 --> 00:04.015
It's car dealership Tube Man in the new Scion iA, ...

00:04.480 --> 00:06.343
...recently liberated and never looking back.

00:06.917 --> 00:08.529
It's weird he'd want a back up camera,...

00:08.799 --> 00:10.393
...well with the whole "never looking back" thing.

00:11.056 --> 00:12.463
And he can barely contain his excitement...

00:12.528 --> 00:14.745
...about the low-speed pre-collision safety system.

00:15.519 --> 00:18.215
It's weird he'd care about a seven-inch touchscreen display...

00:18.465 --> 00:20.573
...when his hands are in the air like you just don't.

00:21.335 --> 00:23.763
But who better to point out all the standard features?

00:25.332 --> 00:26.515
The new Scion iA.

00:26.658 --> 00:28.840
Standard features that actually come standard.

00:29.159 --> 00:29.865
Weird, right?

